Package io.artframework

Interface ResolveContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Scoped
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultResolveContext
    public interface ResolveContext
extends Scoped
    The ResolutionContext holds additional information about the resolution of resolvers and replacement of variables.

    Register your Resolver with the ResolverProvider and your Replacement of variables with the ReplacementProvider.
